7. **finasteride + dutasteride off-label** = 만성 hirsutism — cross-mens_health BPH 약. 5α-reductase isoform 1/2 selectivity 가 양자-VQE fit.
8. **eflornithine Vaniqa 2000** = 만성 hirsutism topical — ornithine decarboxylase 저해 facial hair. 만성 cosmetic + 만성 dermatology overlap.
9. **ovarian drilling laparoscopic** = 만성 surgical clomiphene-resistant. 만성 invasive 한계 + 만성 ovarian reserve 영향 — pharmacological alternative 우선.
